profile: For over 30 years, Saltillo Experts Refinishing has been the premier saltillo and Mexican tile contractor in San Antonio and the surrounding areas. We are proud to offer you second to none saltillo and Mexican tile installation and refinishing. We offer all services for saltillo and Mexican tile from start to finish. We offer installation of saltillo and Mexican tile, restoration, cleaning, stripping, sealing and refinishing services. Our experienced staff will make sure that your tile is looking brand new after we are done with our restoration and refinishing services. Call us today!
